Should I search for the material or for the spiritual April 27, 2018

   Filed under: Shri Mataji ‚Äî Peter @ 12:29 pm
   Tags: material or spiritual, Sahaja yoga, Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,
   Spirit, Spirituality


   Question: I have a search for the material and a search for the
   spiritual, but while I am young should I use it for the search for the
   material or the search for the spiritual?

   Shri_Mataji: If you get the Spirit you get the material automatically.
   The whole material is controlled by the Spirit. Is very surprising how
   you get it. Is you enter into the realm of God. You‚Äôll be amazed that
   in England, there‚Äôs such a lot of joblessness, people don‚Äôt have jobs
   at all, unemployment. See all these words I don‚Äôt know. Unemployment.
   But not a single Sahaja Yogi is unemployed. Not a single Sahaja Yogi is
   unemployed. The other day, one gentleman was to come from Paris to
   Australia for a particular seminar and he thought he wanted to come
   because this is the other side of the world and all that, but quite
   excited. But he didn‚Äôt have money, and suddenly he got the money which
   he wasn‚Äôt to get for eight years. Suddenly he got the money, he is
   here. All such miracles work out. From Australia I‚Äôll tell you one
   miracle that‚Äôs most interesting. There was a little girl, she wrote a
   letter to me: ‚ÄúMother, I want to come and see you in India, but I don‚Äôt
   have so much money to come.‚Äù She and her mother they both wanted to
   come and they had a fete in the school and she had taken a trinket for
   selling and when the teacher saw it she said, ‚ÄúThis is gold, better
   take it to your mother.‚Äù And when they went to the jeweller the amount
   was the same as they would need to go to India. So in so many ways you
   are helped. You don‚Äôt know the realm of God is very different. So
   efficient, works so fast. We haven‚Äôt entered into that realm.
   Public Lecture ‚Äì Brisbane Australia 1987

